 &lt;BR&gt; 
2. The Company operates in a single business segment, i.e., Footwear and Accessories. &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
3. During the quarter and half year ended 30th September 2023, a scheme for voluntary retirement (VRS) was introduced at one manufacturing units and Rs. 409.00 Million was offered for the same and is disclosed as an exceptional item. &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
